{"tid":251370,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［命運自選台］有得比你揀，做個米八肥仔定米六五大隻仔？","createTime":"2017-05-20T22:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T13:40:15.000Z","uid":73722,"like":28,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"adb5ba7e35ddec0171208143b5beb659725b18ea","tid":251370,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T22:01:54.000Z","msg":"巴打們，假設唔理家底同樣，你有得改變自己身形，你會點揀？<br />\n絲打們，假設兩個都咁有錢咁靚仔，你會揀邊個做男友？：<br />\n<br />\n正評：唔著鞋都有米八，肥底，小小突腩兼有士啤呔，有肥仔波，出親街都要縮肚，基因肥點減都減唔到，但hokd得住點食都唔會更肥<br />\n<br />\n負評：著鞋都無米七，但身形fit到漏，肌肉得黎線條靚，唔會一舊舊，加埋一個點食都唔肥既胃<br />\n<br />\n利伸比左個負皮自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廿幾歲就有士啤呔日日dup低頭見到自己對波仲要飛晒釘，點都減唔到真係好想自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95c3b2b8f1aa02733607ebf49546a4f16b09e06","tid":251370,"uid":16650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T22:06:31.000Z","msg":"米八肥仔易有膝蓋關節炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ed33b2bae3310bec424373f2821cbae8716ff7","tid":251370,"uid":103285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T22:20:04.000Z","msg":"好難選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5dd9e90def8206ef2c25754d7577596edffb116","tid":251370,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T22:33:38.000Z","msg":"高質留名"},{"pid":"b04cbf02ce0bf70c9cea1f22fddde42969864a77","tid":251370,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T22:33:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>米八肥仔易有膝蓋關節炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做親運動減肥都係膝頭最快痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afcdf196f2434edf6134c80afd8d63521a0e93e","tid":251370,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T22:35:36.000Z","msg":"開頭跑膝頭痛以為自己係肥得濟，咪諗住減少少食量+做燃脂操，點知所有同下半身有關既動作都係膝頭會痛<img src=\"/assets/fac